  {FDA7B6630DB87991}Prefabs/Items/Equipment/Backpacks/Backpack_M70_Swiss.et        weight:25
  {BBA08EC4EC40FA94}Prefabs/Characters/Uniforms/Jacket_M70.et                     weight:15
